text: A69 or A-69 may refer to: * A69 road (England), a road in England * A69 type, another name for the D'Estienne d'Orves class of French anti-submarine corvettes * Benoni Defense, Encyclopaedia of Chess Openings code * HLA-A69, an HLA-A serotype * Abashiri Station, a station in Abashiri, Hokkaido, Japan, station code A69
title: A69
